    <abstract id="aspace_d8c68eabd26a4b3d2fd951569bd6009d">Founded in 1909 as Broadview Swedish Seminary by the Seventh Day Aventists.  Became Broadview College and Theological Seminary in 1922.  In 1931 it re-organized as a junior college known as Broadview Junior College.  In 1934 merged with other schools to become Broadview Academy.  Closed around 2007.</abstract>
